You're the kind of person who figures it out on your own. You don't have the time or patience to wait through days or weeks of courses. You don't want to pay some stranger thousands of dollars. You need a fast website. Good!
This course was created for you, the smart DIY type who wants a tutorial that gets to the point. Kray will teach you how to build a website without any useless filler information, advertisements or hidden expenses. All of the tools and templates for this course are completely free.
What you'll learn
*How to install Joomla
*How to make it Responsive
